Market Module: This module allows users to simulate current and future trends for the HC markets, allowing them to choose the best market framework aligned with the users economic, environmental and social interests. The outputs of the market analysis enable users (e.g., industries, supermarkets and data centers) to estimate potential costs and revenues for different market participants from trading excess heat and cold.

This software is authored by:
Linde Frölke, A. Sérgio Faria, Tiago Soares, Tiago Sousa

This program makes use and is distributed with the following libraries:
* colorama (https://pypi.org/project/colorama/)
* cvxpy (https://www.cvxpy.org/)
* matplotlib (https://pypi.org/project/matplotlib/)
* numpy (https://numpy.org/)
* pandas (https://pandas.pydata.org/)
* pyscipopt (https://github.com/scipopt/PySCIPOpt/blob/master/LICENSE)
* scipy (https://scipy.org/)

